T ← {"Rosetta" "Code" "is" "a" "programming" "chrestomathy" "site"}
F₁ ← ⧻                       # Sort by length.
F₂ ← ⇌                       # Sort by reversed string.
UiuaSort! ← ⊏⍏≡⍚^!.          # Create the keys, then sort array using them.
Schwartz! ← ≡⊡1⊏⍏≡⊢.≡(⊂⍚^!.) # Adds keys, sorts, then strips them.
UiuaSort!F₁ T
Schwartz!F₁ T
UiuaSort!F₂ T
Schwartz!F₂ T
